      "acceptanceCriteria": "Mesh convergence study demonstrating QoI change less than 5% between successive refinements.",
      "rationale": "Three-level mesh refinement study performed; peak von Mises stress at screw-rod interface changed by 2.1% between medium and fine mesh. Richardson extrapolation applied. Achieved level exceeds required."
