      "acceptanceCriteria": "Documented simulation workflow with independent review of boundary conditions, material assignments, and loading definitions.",
      "rationale": "Simulation protocol reviewed by two independent analysts. Boundary condition definitions cross-checked against ASTM F1717 test fixture geometry. No use errors identified. Required level met."
