      "rationale": "Ti-6Al-4V elastic modulus (114 GPa) and yield strength (880 MPa) from certified material test reports. Screw geometry from CMM measurements with tolerance ±0.01 mm. Input uncertainty propagated via Monte Carlo (n=500). Required level met."
