      "rationale": "Testing performed at single compression-bending load condition per ASTM F1717 protocol. Clinical loading variability not fully explored. Achieved level below required; this factor is identified as a gap in the credibility assessment. Accepted under risk-informed rationale given Class II device classification and conservative load selection."
