      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Validation scenario sufficiently similar to the intended use scenario in terms of geometry, loading, and material to support extrapolation.",
      "rationale": "Validation performed on production-representative constructs under standardized ASTM F1717 conditions directly analogous to the regulatory submission context. Geometric and material similarity between validation and intended use scenarios confirmed. Required level met."
